object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct ClaimTransaction.StatSequence, ClaimTransaction.ClaimsTransactionKey,
ClaimTransaction.ClaimStatSystemId 
FROM
 dbo.ClaimTransaction
 inner join
 dbo.ClaimStats_Stg
 on ClaimTransaction.PolicyKey = ClaimStats_Stg.PolicyNumber + ClaimStats_Stg.PolicyVersion
 and ClaimTransaction.ClaimNumber = Claimstats_Stg.ClaimNumber
 and ClaimTransaction.CoverageCd = Claimstats_Stg.CoverageCd
 and ClaimTransaction.FeatureCd = Claimstats_Stg.FeatureCd
 and ClaimTransaction.ClaimantTransactionNumber = Claimstats_Stg.ClaimantTransactionNumber
 and ClaimTransaction.TransactionNumber = Claimstats_Stg.TransactionNumber
where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31'
